ABB Wins Contract for Eskom Power Station, Business Day Says

-- B y   J a n a   M a r a i s
-- 
2011-09-08T07:58:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/abb-wins-contract-for-eskom-power-station-business-day-says.html
ABB Ltd. (ABBN) , the provider of power and
automation technologies, has won a contract from  South Africa â€™s
state-owned power utility Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd. to provide
equipment for its Arnot power station, Business Day reported.  The 20-month project will include design, production
engineering, factory testing, delivery, installation,
commissioning, operational acceptance testing, plant
documentation and training, Business Day said.  This will fully automate the plant, allow for remote
central operation of the system and improve worker safety,
Business Day reported ABB South Africa Country Manager Carlos Pone as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
